'++LotusScript Development Environment:2:2:BindEvents:1:129
Private Sub BindEvents(Byval Objectname_ As String)
	Static Source As NOTESUIVIEW
	Set Source = Bind(Objectname_)
	On Event Queryaddtofolder From Source Call Queryaddtofolder
	On Event Postopen From Source Call Postopen
End Sub

'++LotusScript Development Environment:2:2:Queryaddtofolder:1:12
Sub Queryaddtofolder(Source As Notesuiview, Target As Variant, Continue As Variant)
	
End Sub
'++LotusScript Development Environment:2:2:Postopen:1:12
Sub Postopen(Source As Notesuiview)
	Dim Session As New NotesSession
	Dim db As NotesDatabase
	Dim CalProfile As NotesDocument
	
	Set db = Session.CurrentDatabase
	Set WS = New notesuiworkspace
	
	Set CalProfile = db.getprofiledocument("CalendarProfile")
	
	'// If Mail Policy's Attention Indicator is applied, let's rebuild the Folder
	If Not (CalProfile Is Nothing) Then
		If CalProfile.HasItem("MPolicy_RebuildInbox") Then
			If CalProfile.GetItemValue("MPolicy_RebuildInbox")(0) = "1" Then				
				Dim currentUser As String
				currentUser = Session.username	
				Dim accPriv As Long	
				accPriv = db.QueryAccessPrivileges(currentUser)		
				If  (( accPriv And DBACL_CREATE_SHARED_FOLDERS_VIEWS ) > 0) Then
					Call ws.viewrebuild( True, True )
					Call ws.viewrefresh
					Call CalProfile.ReplaceItemValue("MPolicy_RebuildInbox", "") '//Reset flag
					Call CalProfile.Save(True,False)						
				End If
			End If	
		End If
	End If	
	
	'Name column sorting
'	Dim shView As String	
'	shView = "i"
	Call NameSortViewPO	
	
End Sub
